[10/02/2019 17:44:53] <font color="#ffffff">Así que esta madre</font>
[10/02/2019 17:44:56] <font color="#ffffff">Yeah! They're on the way!</font>
[10/02/2019 17:44:56] <font color="#ffffff">PAW Patrol, PAW Patrol</font>
[10/02/2019 17:45:00] <font color="#ffffff">yen su camino se topará</font>
